Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然失去意識了 但還有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們的容量被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倖免的似乎只有元神靈和契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的容量流向清淨之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是霧那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法用直升飛機了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.86,0:00:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都從清淨之地開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那裡又有什麼大事發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是命運嗎 可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法從這片茜姐消失的大海中移開自己的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:31.36,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眩く光る汚れに　瞬く事を忘れた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:31.36,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光怪陸離的醜惡　使我忘記了眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.97,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二度と訪れない一瞬に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.97,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕無僅有的的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.89,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠を感じさせた　Death through tRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.89,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感覺彷彿永恆　通向死亡的沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:43.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death through tRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.98,0:01:43.45,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向死亡的沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:52.35,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小説を逆から読むようなXtasy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:52.35,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從最後一頁開始看小說似的狂喜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:59.53,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉と感情がリンクする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:59.53,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言與感情相互連接
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.94,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛したい夜に濡れたいfor me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.94,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像熱戀那般對我發情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:06.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えないようにせめぎあう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:06.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不瞑目般地死纏爛打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:13.21,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪いたいのに遠回りをして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:13.21,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖想豪奪卻仍舊故作姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:17.09,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足りないlogic　溢れるtrick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:17.09,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不充分的邏輯　漫溢的詭計
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.78,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えないように絡み合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.78,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁若無人地相互纏繞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:25.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もういっそこのままtRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:25.75,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了　乾脆就此沉眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.46,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.46,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.74,i,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 17 「真神」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回清淨之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 以你的傷勢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太去找茜姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你沒事啊 慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使茜姐還活著 這樣下去也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我所能做到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這也是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便要衝破它
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我無法取代的搭檔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲以前住在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過我們住在山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 小黑是大小姐 那揶雲也是個人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒沒什麼 不過因為是黎真的大弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈石就在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 走了那麼久你也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 繼續走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 普尼普尼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只蟲子只是受驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普尼普尼 沒馬上幫你也不用那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才感覺到的容量是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太餓睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑也吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普尼普尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了 還以為是敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 吃豆糕嗎 很有營養的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清淨之地不應該有元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是獅子神族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是契約者 你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是娜姆 為了記載歷史來到此地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記載歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們族人代代都是佑筆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑筆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說大陸上有一族元神靈從開天闢地以來一直在記錄歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是歷史轉折的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是來記錄這次轉折的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉折是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為發生了沖繩靈石毀壞 容量暴漲事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:08:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開聖地來發源地日本進行調查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可因為沒錢 以及和機場的人講價失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只好混在貨物裡 好不容易才到了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想知道的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揶雲 你不覺得她很可疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的容量表明她並不是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 全世界的靈石在瞬間都被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的靈石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得 原來是因為全世界靈石裡的容量都聚集到這了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是清淨之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕因為這裡的靈石是靈王石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印著能夠毀滅世界力量的靈石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王石裡封印著真神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在天地初開時從容量中誕生的神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從容量裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄是這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在只有陽光 大地和水的遠古
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從生命之源的容量中誕生了真神 元神靈和人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然三者分別生存在不同的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真神為了得到一切 開始侵犯別的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從元神靈處取走了自然的調和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕裂了人類的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可人類卻在河川和田地上到處設立神祇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真神打算殺掉人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便將人類的容量據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不講理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一己之利強搶豪奪 真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可元神靈把人類看作是與之共存的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是元神靈和人類相互交換心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立契約共同對抗真神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元神靈和人類的契約也是從那時開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真神的戰鬥進行地十分慘烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真神毫不顧忌自己毀滅世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打得天殘地缺 冰海火獄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過了數百年的努力 終於打倒了真神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為了封印他的力量 除了靈王石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還設置了許許多多的靈石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真神在被封印前對人類下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就是 三位一在系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 真神的詛咒導致了人類殘酷的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一在系統是因為詛咒產生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一在系統是為了令人類受苦而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被告知要維持容量均衡和三位一在系統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為主根源增加會導致容量飽和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而使被封印的真神復活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到真神的力量 便能毀滅世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀虎族的阿邏宜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀虎族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和水華魅一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水華魅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個潑婦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打過好幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒輸過就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是覬覦真神的力量而來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單是我們 還有別的人在打真神的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你還活著 獅子神黎真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也覺得打倒了施泰納的你不會那麼輕易被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把真神的力量讓給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙我的人通通要死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宙 同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 阿邏宜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 同步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容量形成了循環
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里央奈小姐 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你還沒恢復到能戰鬥的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻手都有紋章 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有必要一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得能看到有趣的戰鬥 你別搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宙 用Thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地審判
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難得的感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Thousand能夠自由操縱一定範圍內的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續加大重力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要被壓碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠承受這樣的重力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點重力完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了以你的現在的體力什麼也做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然有那麼多容量就上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不還帶著武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能干涉歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能記錄歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我有Thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在重力場中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從下往上 攻擊威力減半
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上往下 攻擊威力加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說一定要利用重力加速度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害的Thousand 但還是我的拳頭更勝一籌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打哪呢 想殺了自己的搭檔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 從上面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 滅牙得救世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然從上往下打攻擊力會翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是 可是 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒被這麼打過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真耐打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪裡的元神靈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅子神族的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是獅子神的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 獸魔裝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從和水華魅戰鬥以來 阿邏宜還是頭次動真格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力場中 還沒誰能頂過一分鐘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 這樣下去小黑要輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到你粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 慶太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 滅牙得救世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒了重力場 但這種程度的超越技還是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑 別退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 犧我得救世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不愧是獅子神的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和黎真打算聯手染指真神的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿邏宜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在回來的時候便感覺到了哥哥的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他的容量怎麼用不完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍 戰鬥結束後 一起回尼斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候求婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越技 群魔亂舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不清楚 大意不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝恩哈德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿了 時候終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了 哥哥的容量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說黎真果真在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我也感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真也想得到真神的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會讓他得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真正往靈王石那去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去哥哥那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我們真能打倒黎真嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:35.25,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狂ほし月の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:35.25,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光狂亂地灑向大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:42.44,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一恵み胸に受けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:42.44,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身體感受這上天的恩澤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:48.20,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌おう　歌おう　囁いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:48.20,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱吧　唱吧　輕聲唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:54.51,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踊ろう　踊ろう　一緒に　Pa.Dis.Thu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:54.51,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳吧　跳吧　一起　Pa.Dis.Thu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:22:06.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朽ちた楽園で　契りを誓えば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:22:06.29,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能在枯朽的樂園締結誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:18.24,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀のドレス　月色に染まるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:18.24,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮服也染上了銀色的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾克塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連貝恩哈德也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被黎真殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此 他的容量我一輩子也忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎真應該也受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是打倒他的最佳時機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不會白死的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:06.45,o,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode 「異變」
